@baseUrl = http://localhost:8040
@apiKey = dev-demo-key

### Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Coaching request
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/coach
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "alex@contoso.com",
  "role": "it",
  "goal": "Improve incident triage productivity",
  "skill_level": "intermediate"
}

### Log adoption event
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/adoption/events
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "alex@contoso.com",
  "department": "IT",
  "action": "Used Copilot to summarize incident"
}

### Metrics
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/adoption/metrics
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
